channel.title: Entrana || PI || Release || Explicity V2
channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/5cccc2.png[/img][/center]
Hey, I am done with Entrana as I got bored and I have started a new development called Zanaris and found a better base to use. Anyways on this I used Caution-X which is the one I used for Explicity V1, And this time I fixed drops, fixed unarmed attack animations, Added new working hits with the proper HP Bars and you can still select from New HP bar Or Old. I added Dicing from the one in V1, I fixed bugs and glitches. I fixed slayer master so it gives tasks. I added proper animations for Yaks. I changed teleports for training I done a lot more but I just can't list as I done a lot on this base.
Added a really small and easy anti - leech if you cannot fix it I am sorry you shouldn't try using this base as it is the most simplest anti leech in the world. If you fix you can tell others how to fix I don't mind but I just put it to stop leechers mainly.
You can use this if you want, Please don't flame I didn't spend too much time on this but I did get a lot done. Also new development is called Zanaris.
Links: Source/Client - Package: http://uppit.com/tvlxuwkbgxha/Entrana_Package.zip Cache: (Auto downloads but if you want to download manually put it in C:) - https://dl.dropbox.com/u/84386870/Entranav1cache.zip
Thanks, RS PS
Also big thanks to ah_rule for his tutorial on hitmarks helped me a lot in this development.
[img]http://i42.tinypic.com/uvwuc.png[/img] [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/erg3eu.png[/img] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/kbegdu.png[/img] [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/34p1gdx.png[/img] [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/2rqogzr.png[/img]
